(1, 'Baskonia Vitoria-Gasteiz', 'Euroleague', 14, 8, 83.5, 79.2, 35.0, 17.2, 6.8, 3.2, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'The team was founded in 1959 in the Vitorija-Gasteiz city.\r\n• The team has won the Spanish Championship (ACB) 8 times, including a victory over FC Barcelona in 2020.\r\n• They have won the Spanish Copa del Rey 6 times.\r\n• They have won the Spanish Supercup 4 times.\r\n• They have been EuroLeague finalists 3 times and have reached the Final Four 6 times.\r\n• Although they have not won the EuroLeague, they are considered a strong and respected basketball club.\r\n', '/images/Baskonia Vitoria-Gasteiz.png'),
(2, 'Real Madrid', 'Euroleague', 18, 4, 88.2, 75.3, 37.5, 19.1, 7.3, 3.9, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 14:58:31', 'Ispanijos krepšinio komanda iš Madrido, priklausanti „Real“ sporto klubui. Ši komanda tituluočiausia Europoje. Krepšinio klubas įkurtas 1931m.\r\n•	Ši komanda tapo 11 kartų Europos taurės laimėtoja.\r\n(1964 m. 1965 m. 1967 m. 1968 m. 1974 m. 1978 m. 1980 m. 1995 m. 2015 m. 2018 m. 2023 m.). \r\n•	FIBA tarpžemyninė taurė – 3 kartus.\r\n(1976 m. 1977 m. 1978 m. )\r\n•	Daugkartinė Ispanijos taurės laimėtoja. 29 laimėjimai.\r\n ', '/images/Real Madrid.png'),
(3, 'FC Barcelona', 'Euroleague', 17, 5, 86.9, 76.2, 36.9, 18.7, 7.0, 3.7, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 14:59:09', 'The Spanish basketball team from Barcelona. Founded in 1926, this team is one of the most successful in Europe.\r\n• The team has won the Spanish Championship (ACB) 20 times. They have also claimed the Spanish King\s Cup (Copa del Rey) 27 times.\r\n• They have won the EuroLeague twice (in 2003 and 2010) and have reached the Final Four numerous times.\r\n• They have won the FIBA Europe Cup once.\r\n', '/images/FC Barcelona.png'),
(4, 'Paris Basketball', 'Euroleague', 16, 6, 85.3, 77.8, 36.2, 18.1, 6.9, 3.5, '2025-05-13 12:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'A very young basketball club, founded only in 2018 in Paris.\r\n• In 2021, the team was promoted to Pro A (the top French league).\r\n• In 2023, they became EuroCup champions and earned a spot in the 2024 EuroLeague season.\r\n', '/images/Paris Basketball.png'),
(5, 'Olympiacos Piraeus', 'Euroleague', 15, 7, 84.1, 78.4, 35.8, 17.5, 6.5, 3.3, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'The basketball club was founded in 1931 in the city of Piraeus, Greece.\r\n• The team has won the Greek Championship (Greek Basket League) 13 times and the Greek Cup 11 times.\r\n• In the EuroLeague, the team has been crowned champions 3 times (1997, 2012, 2013) and has been runners-up 4 more times (2010, 2015, 2017, 2023).\r\n• In 2013, the team won the Intercontinental Cup, defeating the Brazilian team Pinheiros Sky in the final.\r\n', '/images/Olympiacos Piraeus.png'),
(6, 'Fenerbahce Beko Istanbul', 'Euroleague', 14, 8, 83.8, 78.9, 35.5, 17.3, 6.4, 3.2, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'The basketball club was founded in 1913 in Istanbul, Turkey. It is one of the most successful basketball clubs in Europe.\r\n• The team has won the Turkish Championship 10 times, the Turkish Cup 7 times, and the Turkish Supercup also 7 times.\r\n• In 2017, they became EuroLeague champions. They were runners-up in 2016 and 2018, and reached the Final Four every year from 2015 to 2019.\r\n', '/images/Fenerbahce Beko Istanbul.png'),
(7, 'Anadolu Efes Istanbul', 'Euroleague', 15, 7, 84.5, 78.1, 35.9, 17.7, 6.7, 3.4, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'The basketball club was founded in 1976 in Istanbul. Initially named \"Efes Pilsen,\" it was renamed Anadolu Efes in 2011.\r\n• The team has won the Turkish Championship 16 times, the Turkish Cup 12 times, and the Turkish Supercup 13 times.\r\n• They became EuroLeague champions in 2021 and 2022, and were runners-up in 2019.\r\n• In 1996, they were EuroCup champions.\r\n', '/images/Anadolu Efes Istanbul.png'),
(8, 'Maccabi Playtica Tel Aviv', 'Euroleague', 13, 9, 82.7, 79.5, 34.8, 16.9, 6.3, 3.0, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'Maccabi Playtika Tel Aviv is a basketball team from Israel, founded in 1932.\r\n• The team has won the Israeli Championship over 50 times and the Israeli Cup more than 40 times.\r\n• Maccabi has won the EuroLeague 6 times (1977, 1981, 2001, 2004, 2005, 2014) and reached the Final Four over 15 times.\r\n• In 2014, they defeated Real Madrid in overtime to win their latest EuroLeague title.\r\n• The club is one of the most successful and recognized basketball teams in Europe.', '/images/Maccabi Playtica Tel Aviv.png'),
(9, 'Panathinaikos AKTOR Athens', 'Euroleague', 12, 10, 81.5, 80.3, 34.2, 16.4, 6.1, 2.9, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'The basketball club was founded in 1919 in Athens, Greece. The team is one of the most decorated basketball clubs in all of European history.\r\n\r\nThe team has won the Greek Championship (Greek Basket League) 39 times and the Greek Cup 20 times.\r\n\r\nIn the EuroLeague, the team has been crowned champions 6 times (1996, 2000, 2002, 2007, 2009, 2011). They have reached the Final Four 11 times.\r\n\r\nIn 1996, the team won the Intercontinental Cup, defeating the Argentine team Olimpia de Venado Tuerto in the final.\r\n', '/images/Panathinaikos AKTOR Athens.png'),
(10, 'FC Bayern Munich', 'Euroleague', 11, 11, 80.4, 80.9, 33.8, 16.1, 5.9, 2.8, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'The basketball club was founded in 1946 in Munich, Germany.\r\n• The team has won the German Championship (Basketball Bundesliga) 5 times and the German Cup (BBL-Pokal) 4 times.\r\n• In the EuroLeague, they have reached the quarterfinals twice and were EuroCup finalists in 2018.\r\n', '/images/FC Bayern Munich.png'),
(11, 'LDLC ASVEL Villeurbanne', 'Euroleague', 10, 12, 79.2, 81.8, 33.3, 15.7, 5.7, 2.6, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'The club was founded in 1948 in Villeurbanne, France.\r\n\r\n• The team has won the French Championship (LNB Pro A) 20 times and the French Cup (Coupe de France) 9 times.\r\n• In 1997, they were EuroLeague finalists but lost in the final.\r\n• In 2001, they won the EuroCup.\r\n', '/images/LDLC ASVEL Villeurbanne.png'),
(12, 'EA7 Emporio Armani Milan', 'Euroleague', 13, 9, 82.1, 79.8, 34.6, 16.7, 6.2, 3.0, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'One of the most renowned and successful basketball teams in Italy. Founded in Milan, Italy, in 1936.\r\n\r\n• The team has won the Italian Championship (Lega Basket Serie A) 30 times.\r\n• They are three-time EuroLeague champions (1966, 1987, 1988) and have been runners-up twice (1967, 1983).\r\n• FIBA Intercontinental Cup winners in 1987.\r\n• They have won the Italian Cup (Coppa Italia) 8 times and the Italian Supercup 4 times.\r\n', '/images/EA7 Emporio Armani Milan.png'),
(13, 'Partizan Mozzart Bet Belgrade', 'Euroleague', 12, 10, 81.8, 80.1, 34.4, 16.5, 6.0, 2.8, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'A basketball club from Belgrade, Serbia, founded in 1945.\r\n• The team has won the Serbian Championship 22 times and the Serbian Cup 10 times.\r\n• They have won the international ABA League (Adriatic League) 6 times.\r\n• In 2014, the team reached the EuroCup final but lost to Valencia Basket. In the EuroLeague, they have reached the Top 16 several times but have not achieved significant success.\r\n', '/images/Partizan Mozzart Bet Belgrade.png'),
(14, 'AS Monaco', 'Euroleague', 14, 8, 83.2, 79.4, 35.2, 17.0, 6.5, 3.1, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:06:36', 'The basketball team was founded in 1928 in Monaco.\r\n\r\n• In 2023, they won the LNB Pro A title, defeating ASVEL Villeurbanne in the final.\r\n• The team won the French Cup (Coupe de France) in 2023.\r\n• In 2021, they won the EuroCup.\r\n• The 2022 season was their first in the EuroLeague, where they reached the quarterfinals. In 2023, they advanced to the Final Four and finished in third place.\r\n', '/images/AS Monaco.png'),
(15, 'Virtus Segafredo Bologna', 'Euroleague', 11, 11, 80.7, 80.5, 34.0, 16.3, 5.8, 2.7, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'One of the most renowned Italian basketball clubs in Europe, founded in 1929 in Bologna, Italy.\r\n• The team has won the Italian Championship (Lega Basket Serie A) 16 times.\r\n• They are two-time EuroLeague champions (1998, 2001) and have been runners-up twice (1981, 2002).\r\n• EuroCup champions in 2022.\r\n• They have won the Italian Cup (Coppa Italia) 8 times and the Italian Supercup 4 times.\r\n', '/images/Virtus Segafredo Bologna.png'),
(16, 'Crvena Zvezda', 'Euroleague', 10, 12, 79.5, 81.2, 33.5, 15.9, 5.6, 2.5, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:17:51', 'The basketball club was founded in 1945 in Belgrade, Serbia.\r\n• The team has won the Serbian Championship (KLS – Košarkaška liga Srbije) 20 times.\r\n• In 2019, the club won the Balkan Cup.\r\n• They were EuroLeague champions in 1992 and EuroCup winners in 2018.\r\n', '/images/Crvena Zvezda.png'),
(17, 'ALBA Berlin', 'Euroleague', 9, 13, 78.6, 82.1, 33.0, 15.5, 5.4, 2.4, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:02:57', 'The basketball club was founded in 1991 in Berlin, Germany.\r\n• The team has won the German Championship (Basketball Bundesliga) 11 times and the German Cup (BBL-Pokal) 11 times.\r\n• In Europe, they won the FIBA Korać Cup in 1995.\r\n• They have not reached the EuroLeague Final Four.\r\n', '/images/ALBA Berlin.png'),
(18, 'Žalgiris Kaunas', 'Euroleague', 8, 14, 77.8, 82.8, 32.7, 15.2, 5.2, 2.3, '2025-05-13 15:17:44', '2025-05-17 15:05:59', 'Žalgiris is a Lithuanian basketball team from Kaunas, founded on October 13, 1944.\r\n\r\nIn 1985, Žalgiris defeated CSKA Moscow and became USSR champions.\r\n\r\nIn 1999, Žalgiris became European champions. In the final, they defeated Kinder Bologna 82–74. This is Žalgiris\ greatest achievement in the EuroLeague.\r\n\r\nIn 2005, they reached the FIBA Europe Cup quarterfinals.\r\n\r\nIn 2018, they won third place in the EuroLeague. A loss to Fenerbahçe Istanbul (67–76) prevented them from reaching a higher position.\r\n\r\nThe 2022 season was very unsuccessful, with only 8 wins out of 34 games.', '/images/Žalgiris Kaunas.png');

